data.description: Awesome opportunity for a  home owner or investor. This awesome home has new paint, newer floors and a great kitchen. Enter through the the spacious front outdoor porch to an amazing living room. The dedicated dining area leads to the  the kitchen. The rear yard is spacious providing outside entertaining space. The upper level presents 3 full bedrooms and a full bath. The bedrooms are spacious and provide closet space. There is a full unfinished basement, tons of space great heater and hot water heater. Just minutes from center city Philadelphia and the Western suburbs .  Definitely a great opportunity.
